cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.HC, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with video quality assessment, which involves computer vision and image processing techniques (cs.CV). It also involves quantifying subjective human perception (cs.HC) and designing a prediction method using machine learning (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses statistical modeling (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT) in the context of just-noticeable-difference (JND) visual perception property.
